    ns1:otherInformation "The planning described might be slightly affected by daily adjustments. There is not a clear distinction between theoretical and problem or practical classes since the idea is to have the theoretical presentations intermingled with practical implementations and exercises, side by side, perhaps inside the same session."@es ;
    ns1:periodEndingMonth "Enero"@es ;
